condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Section 2a1 | Description :Prepare project reports. Each report shall cover the period of one quarter of theEthiopian Fiscal Year, and shall be furnished to IDA not later than 60 days after the end of the reporting period | Frequency:Quarterly
Finance Agreement :Section2a2 | Description :Carry out joint review of the progress of project implementation at regular intervalswith donor partners financing the program. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :Section2a3 | Description :Carry out mid term review of progress carried out under the project and furnish reportto the Association | Due Date :30-Jun-2012

Finance Agreement :SectionIIB2 | Description :Prepare and furnish to IDA not less than 60 days after the end of each quarter,interim un-audited financial reports for each of the respective parts of the project covering the period | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :SectionIIB3 | Description :Project Audit shall cover the period of one FY of the Recipient. The Audit shall befurnished to IDA not later than 6 months after the end of such period | Frequency :Yearly
